10. Checking if two words are anagrams

filter_none
edit
play_arrow

brightness_5
from collections import Counter 
def is_anagram(str1, str2): 
     return Counter(str1) == Counter(str2) 
print(is_anagram('geek', 'eegk')) 
  
print(is_anagram('geek', 'peek'))     
Output:
True
False





